                               INSTALL

1. Unpack the archive with components

2. Install ZCommonXXX and ZDbwareXXX packages from
  Zeos Database Objects library

3. Edit Zeos.inc file. You may set there you language,
  maximum quantity of supported memo fields, etc.

4. Add to Delphi Library Path pathes to 
  XXX, XXX\utils, XXX\dbctrls, where XXX - ZeosCtrl directory.

2. Compile and install library in Delphi 3.0, 4.0, 5.0 and
  C++ Builder 4.0 with the same version of dpk file. 
  Install dpk files in the following
  sequence: ZUtilsXXX, ZDbCtrlsXXX
